<!-- ============================================================
     SERVICES PAGE
     ============================================================ -->
<div id="page-services" class="page">
  <div class="page-hero" style="background:var(--ink2)">
    <div class="page-hero-bg">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?w=1400&q=70&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Technology circuit board">
      <div class="page-hero-vignette"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <div class="ph-num">SERVICES / CAPABILITIES</div>
      <div class="label" data-reveal><div class="label-line"></div><span class="label-text">What We Offer</span></div>
      <h2 class="title" data-reveal data-delay="1">Full-spectrum IT solutions for <em>modern enterprises</em></h2>
      <p class="subtitle" data-reveal data-delay="2">We don't just build systems — we build competitive advantage. Every service is delivered by certified specialists who understand both the technology and the business context behind it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section id="svc-page" style="padding-top:60px">
    <div class="svc-list">
      <div class="svc-item" data-reveal>
        <div class="svc-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?w=700&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Custom software development coding"></div>
        <div class="svc-hover-bar"></div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <div class="svc-num2">01 / CUSTOM SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT</div>
          <div class="svc-t">Custom Software Development</div>
          <p class="svc-d">Bespoke applications engineered to your exact operational requirements. From CRM and ERP platforms to client portals and SaaS products — we architect and build software that scales with your business and integrates seamlessly into your existing ecosystem.</p>
          <div class="svc-tags2"><span class="stag">Web Apps</span><span class="stag">Mobile</span><span class="stag">REST APIs</span><span class="stag">ERP/CRM</span><span class="stag">SaaS Platforms</span><span class="stag">Portals</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-item" data-reveal data-delay="1">
        <div class="svc-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544197150-b99a580bb7a8?w=700&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Cloud computing data center"></div>
        <div class="svc-hover-bar"></div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <div class="svc-num2">02 / CLOUD INFRASTRUCTURE & DEVOPS</div>
          <div class="svc-t">Cloud Infrastructure & DevOps</div>
          <p class="svc-d">Architect robust, secure, and cost-optimised cloud environments. We manage migrations, implement CI/CD pipelines, containerise workloads, and provide ongoing infrastructure management across AWS, Azure, and GCP with guaranteed SLA uptime.</p>
          <div class="svc-tags2"><span class="stag">AWS</span><span class="stag">Azure</span><span class="stag">GCP</span><span class="stag">Kubernetes</span><span class="stag">Terraform</span><span class="stag">Docker</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-item" data-reveal>
        <div class="svc-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563013544-824ae1b704d3?w=700&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Cybersecurity data protection"></div>
        <div class="svc-hover-bar"></div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <div class="svc-num2">03 / CYBERSECURITY & COMPLIANCE</div>
          <div class="svc-t">Cybersecurity & Compliance</div>
          <p class="svc-d">Comprehensive security posture management. We conduct penetration testing, implement zero-trust architectures, ensure regulatory compliance (NDPR, GDPR, PCI-DSS), and provide 24/7 SOC threat monitoring and incident response.</p>
          <div class="svc-tags2"><span class="stag">Pen Testing</span><span class="stag">NDPR</span><span class="stag">SOC 24/7</span><span class="stag">Zero Trust</span><span class="stag">ISO 27001</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-item" data-reveal data-delay="1">
        <div class="svc-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=700&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Data analytics dashboard charts"></div>
        <div class="svc-hover-bar"></div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <div class="svc-num2">04 / DATA ENGINEERING & ANALYTICS</div>
          <div class="svc-t">Data Engineering & Analytics</div>
          <p class="svc-d">Transform raw data into strategic intelligence. We build data warehouses, real-time streaming pipelines, and interactive dashboards that empower leadership to make evidence-based decisions at speed and with confidence.</p>
          <div class="svc-tags2"><span class="stag">Power BI</span><span class="stag">Tableau</span><span class="stag">Snowflake</span><span class="stag">dbt</span><span class="stag">Kafka</span><span class="stag">Spark</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-item" data-reveal>
        <div class="svc-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?w=700&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="IT strategy consulting meeting"></div>
        <div class="svc-hover-bar"></div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <div class="svc-num2">05 / IT STRATEGY & DIGITAL TRANSFORMATION</div>
          <div class="svc-t">IT Strategy & Digital Transformation</div>
          <p class="svc-d">Executive-level advisory for organisations navigating technology change. We produce IT roadmaps, vendor selection frameworks, operating model redesign, and business cases that align technology investment to commercial outcomes.</p>
          <div class="svc-tags2"><span class="stag">Roadmapping</span><span class="stag">Change Mgmt</span><span class="stag">Architecture</span><span class="stag">TOGAF</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-item" data-reveal data-delay="1">
        <div class="svc-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?w=700&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Managed IT services network monitoring"></div>
        <div class="svc-hover-bar"></div>
        <div class="svc-body">
          <div class="svc-num2">06 / MANAGED IT SERVICES</div>
          <div class="svc-t">Managed IT Services & Support</div>
          <p class="svc-d">24/7 managed support, infrastructure monitoring, helpdesk, and proactive maintenance. We operate as your extended IT department — available, reliable, and always ahead of the curve — backed by iron-clad SLAs.</p>
          <div class="svc-tags2"><span class="stag">Helpdesk</span><span class="stag">SLA-backed</span><span class="stag">Monitoring</span><span class="stag">ITSM</span><span class="stag">ITIL</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="svc-process">
    <div class="label" data-reveal><div class="label-line"></div><span class="label-text">Our Process</span></div>
    <h2 class="title" data-reveal data-delay="1" style="max-width:500px">How we <em>work</em> with every client</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:start">
      <div class="process-timeline" data-reveal>
        <div class="pt-step"><div class="pt-dot"><div class="pt-dot-inner"></div></div><div class="pt-num">01</div><div class="pt-title">Discovery & Diagnosis</div><p class="pt-text">Structured workshops, stakeholder interviews, and technical audits. We develop a clear picture of your current state, constraints, and strategic objectives before any work begins.</p></div>
        <div class="pt-step"><div class="pt-dot"><div class="pt-dot-inner"></div></div><div class="pt-num">02</div><div class="pt-title">Solution Architecture</div><p class="pt-text">Detailed blueprints, technology selection rationale, and risk assessments — giving you full visibility and sign-off before a single line of code is written.</p></div>
        <div class="pt-step"><div class="pt-dot"><div class="pt-dot-inner"></div></div><div class="pt-num">03</div><div class="pt-title">Agile Delivery</div><p class="pt-text">Two-week sprints with structured demos. You always know exactly where your project stands. Scope changes are managed transparently, without surprises.</p></div>
        <div class="pt-step"><div class="pt-dot"><div class="pt-dot-inner"></div></div><div class="pt-num">04</div><div class="pt-title">Deployment & Stabilisation</div><p class="pt-text">A dedicated stabilisation period post-launch ensures performance benchmarks are met and your team is fully trained and confident.</p></div>
        <div class="pt-step"><div class="pt-dot"><div class="pt-dot-inner"></div></div><div class="pt-num">05</div><div class="pt-title">Continuous Improvement</div><p class="pt-text">Ongoing monitoring, quarterly business reviews, and roadmap planning keep your systems healthy, secure, and aligned with your organisation's direction.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal data-delay="2">
        <div class="img-wrap" style="height:400px;margin-bottom:2rem">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?w=700&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Team working on project planning">
          <div class="img-overlay"></div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--ink);padding:2rem;border-left:3px solid var(--gold)">
          <p style="font-family:var(--ff-display);font-style:italic;font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--white);line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:1rem">"Technology is only as valuable as the business outcomes it enables. We measure our success entirely in those terms."</p>
          <span style="font-family:var(--ff-mono);font-size:0.72rem;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:1px">— Michael Omotayo, Founder & CEO</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

