      <h2 class="title" data-reveal data-delay="1">Ideas that <em>move</em><br>the industry forward.</h2>
      <p class="subtitle" data-reveal data-delay="2">Expert perspectives on enterprise technology, cloud strategy, cybersecurity, data, and digital transformation — written by the practitioners doing the work.</p>
      <div class="blog-hero-cats" data-reveal data-delay="3">
